<bibRefCitation author="Metallinou, M. &amp; Arnold, E. N. &amp; Crochet, P. A. &amp; Geniez, P. &amp; Brito, J. C. &amp; Lymberakis, P. &amp; Baha El Din, S. &amp; Sindaco, R. &amp; Robinson, M. &amp; Carranza, S." box="[274,530,1303,1328]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" pagination="258" refId="ref59051" refString="Metallinou, M., Arnold, E. N., Crochet, P. A., Geniez, P., Brito, J. C., Lymberakis, P., Baha El Din, S., Sindaco, R., Robinson, M. &amp; Carranza, S. (2012) Conquering the Sahara and Arabian deserts: systematics and biogeography of Stenodactylus geckos (Reptilia: Gekkonidae). BMC Evolutionary Biology, 12, 258. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1186 / 1471 - 2148 - 12 - 258" type="journal article" year="2012">
Metallinou 
<emphasis box="[406,462,1303,1328]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">et al.</emphasis>
2012
</bibRefCitation>
